  "detailed_description": "Tyraels Ascension: Hell Walker - The Video Game, is a short action adventure game with lite RPG elements that focuses on boss fights, finding player upgrades, replayable levels, key collection, and many hidden secrets. It is based off of the music from the metalcore band \"Tyraels Ascension\" on Rottweiler records. The game tells the prequel to the story laid out in the bands album \"Hell Walker.\" With all of the music in the game being songs from their debut album transformed into \"chip-tune\" versions.",
  "about_the_game": "Tyraels Ascension: Hell Walker - The Video Game, is a short action adventure game with lite RPG elements that focuses on boss fights, finding player upgrades, replayable levels, key collection, and many hidden secrets. It is based off of the music from the metalcore band \"Tyraels Ascension\" on Rottweiler records. The game tells the prequel to the story laid out in the bands album \"Hell Walker.\" With all of the music in the game being songs from their debut album transformed into \"chip-tune\" versions.",
